"surfaceType":357},{"title":588,"body":589,"divs":590,"images":606},"ISic001348. Epitaph for Aurelios Restoutos and Zosime","  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001348_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001348_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001348.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001348-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"edition\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div\">\u003Ca id=\"al1\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[..?]ΛΥΡΗΛΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al2\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[.]ΣΡΕΣΤΟΥΤΟΣ\u003Cbr id=\"al3\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΚΑΙΖΩΣΙΜΗ\u003Cbr id=\"al4\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΗΓΟΡΑΣΟΜΕΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al5\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[.]ΚΤΩΝΙΓΕΙΩΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al6\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[....?..]ΝΕΝΒΑΣΙΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Α | l.5 δ\u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Ferrua, Korhonen: ((Chi-rho)); Kaibel: Μ(ᾶρκος)\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Franz: Ῥεστ[ιτ]οῦτος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"4\">4: \u003Cspan>Franz: ἠγοράσαμεν; Kaibel, Wessel, Korhonen: ἠγοράσομεν (“mixto imperfecto et aoristo ortum” Kaibel, see also IG 14.96)\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"5\">5: \u003Cspan>Franz: ἰίων; Kaibel, Wessel, Korhonen: ἰείων\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"6\">6: \u003Cspan>Franz: ν βάσιν; Kaibel suggested in apparatus ἐν πᾶκι? and Wessel ἐν .ac (see also ἐν πάκης in IGCVO 602); Ferrua [ἠμι]ν ἔνβασιν; Korhonen [ἠμι]ν [?] ἔνβασιν (but also τὴ]ν is possible)\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>((Chi-Rho)) Aurelios Rhestoutos and Zosime, we purchased this tomb at our expense.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>((Chi-Rho)) Aurelios Rhestoutos e Zosime, acquistammo questa tomba a nostre spese.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>This is a marble plaque and not a sarcophagus, which must have served to mark a “loculus”, according to the interpretation that J. and L. Robert (BE 1964 nr. 631) gave for a similar inscription from Catania, RAC 8 (1931) 122-25 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001547\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001547\u003C/a>. This inscription attests to the purchase of the tomb by the deceased who are buried in it: the names of the deceased are followed by the verb \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἀγοράω\u003C/span>, an expression indicating that the purchase was made at their own expense (\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἐκ τῶν ἰδίων\u003C/span>) and by the object (for \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ἔνβασις\u003C/span> as the tomb, see AE 1996.0792 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001423\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001423\u003C/a> and Ferrua 1958: 172). It is possible that there was a reflexive pronoun in the lacuna of l. 6, as in other cases where the deceased purchased the grave for himself: IMusCatania 229 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001628\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001628\u003C/a>. For the registration of the purchase of the tomb in Christian epitaphs, see Führer and Schultze (1907: 12-15) and Korhonen (2004: 108-110). The cognomen of the deceased must have been Restitutus but for such a form, see ICUR 19782. The name of the woman, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Ζωσίμη\u003C/span>, is attested in other inscriptions of the city (CIL 10.7016 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000300\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000300\u003C/a>, IMusCatania 165 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001649\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001649\u003C/a>) and more in general of Sicily (LGPN 3A: 190).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>  \u003Cli> Amico 1741 259 no.15 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> Torremuzza 1769 166 no.19 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> Torremuzza 1784 173 no.19 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> Ferrara 1829 349 no.1 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli>  \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">14.0529\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> 176 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> 3.5723 with p.1250 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001252\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001252\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> Ferrua 1989 no.437 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> 856 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>  \u003Cli> 1964.0631 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1958 172 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001998\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001998\u003C/a>\u003C/li>  \u003Cli> Führer and Schultze 1907 12-15 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001979\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001979\u003C/a>\u003C/li>    \u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[591,593,595,597,599,601,603],{"id":370,"html":592},"\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div\">\u003Ca id=\"al1\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[..?]ΛΥΡΗΛΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al2\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[.]ΣΡΕΣΤΟΥΤΟΣ\u003Cbr id=\"al3\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>ΚΑΙΖΩΣΙΜΗ\u003Cbr id=\"al4\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>ΗΓΟΡΑΣΟΜΕΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al5\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[.]ΚΤΩΝΙΓΕΙΩΝ\u003Cbr id=\"al6\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[....?..]ΝΕΝΒΑΣΙΝ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Α | l.5 δ\u003C/p>",{"id":428,"html":594},"\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>